# An example acl file to control the DAOS pool's accessibility
# This acl file gives everyone under "scitestbed" group to create its own container.
#
# When create the pool (`dmg`), create with option "--group=scitestbed"
# After creating the pool, update the acl with "daos -d pool update-acl -a <this-acl-file> <pool_label>"
#
# Owner: xmei@
# Owner Group: scitestbed@
# Entries:
A::OWNER@:rw
A:G:GROUP@:rw
A:G:scitestbed@:rw
